h4. Actor:
Director, Project Director, Chief Financial Officer.

h4. Description:
This is landing page of "Budget Line Item" Report with search panel on top.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks  [Budget|guide:renderBudgetMenu] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Report" sub menu from left menu.
* Click "Budget" link.
* Show Landing Page of "Project Wise Budget" Report.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show project budget" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get project list in drop-down.[Populate Project List|application]


h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Reset input form on top to search report.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

